we return to restore the balance.

1256
01:46:23,650 --> 01:46:25,200
哥谭还没不可救药
Gotham isn't beyond saving.

1257
01:46:26,530 --> 01:46:29,200
再给我一些时间  这儿还有好人
Give me more time. There are good people here.

1258
01:46:29,410 --> 01:46:31,200
你还在维护这么腐败的城市
You're defending a city so corrupt

1259
01:46:31,410 --> 01:46:34,580
她的所有机构已被我们层层渗透
we have infiltrated every level of its infrastructure.

1260
01:46:45,680 --> 01:46:47,050
该上场了
Time to play.

1261
01:46:51,220 --> 01:46:53,890
我在那座监狱里发现你时  你迷失了方向
When I found you in that jail, you were lost.

1262
