可我对你有信心
But I believed in you.

1263
01:46:56,350 --> 01:47:00,060
我赶走了你的恐惧  为你指出一条路
I took away your fear, and I showed you a path.

1264
01:47:00,360 --> 01:47:02,570
你是我最棒的学生
You were my greatest student.

1265
01:47:02,900 --> 01:47:06,030
你本该待在我的身边  并肩拯救世界
It should be you standing by my side, saving the world.

1266
01:47:06,860 --> 01:47:09,450
我要待在我该待的地方
I'll be standing where I belong.

1267
01:47:10,120 --> 01:47:13,200
在你和哥谭的人民之间
Between you and the people of Gotham.

1268
01:47:14,910 --> 01:47:17,500
没人能救哥谭
No one can save Gotham.

1269
01:47:20,880 --> 01:47:25,510
