1284
01:48:13,600 --> 01:48:17,140
你就像你父亲  缺乏勇气去做你必须做的事
Like your father, you lack the courage to do all that is necessary.

1285
01:48:17,480 --> 01:48:20,310
如果有人阻碍真正的正义
If someone stands in the way of true justice

1286
01:48:20,520 --> 01:48:24,570
