How many from maximum security?

1296
01:49:16,740 --> 01:49:17,740
他们全都逃了
Every one of them.

1297
01:49:17,910 --> 01:49:19,700
连环杀手  强奸犯
Serial killers, rapists.

1298
01:49:19,910 --> 01:49:22,750
让他们把桥升起来  谁都不能逃出这个岛
Raise the bridges. We don't want any getting off the island.

1299
