好  我会去办的
Yeah, I'll raise the bridges

1300
01:49:24,540 --> 01:49:28,750
等我先把所有警力调回来  抓住那些变态杀人狂
when I get every available unit out here to catch the homicidal maniacs

1301
01:49:28,960 --> 01:49:31,800
他们逃得正欢呢  快点
that are running loose out there. Come on!

1302
01:49:55,030 --> 01:49:57,780
但愿你不是消防大队的一员
I hope you're not a member of the fire brigade.

1303
01:50:03,790 --> 01:50:05,880
韦恩少爷  韦恩少爷
Master Wayne! Master Wayne!

1304
01:50:10,420 --> 01:50:14,800
你做那些俯卧撑有什么用  如果连根该死的木头都抬不起
What is the point of all those pushups if you can't even lift a bloody log?

1305
01:50:53,260 --> 01:50:55,300
我都干了些什么呀
What have I done, Alfred?

1306
01:50:56,340 --> 01:50:58,260
家族的一切
Everything my family

1307
01:50:58,470 --> 01:51:00,350
父亲的心血
my father, built

1308
01:51:02,770 --> 01:51:06,640
韦恩的遗产不光是砖头和水泥  少爷
The Wayne legacy is more than bricks and mortar, sir.

1309
01:51:06,850 --> 01:51:09,060
我本想拯救哥谭
I wanted to save Gotham.

1310
01:51:09,940 --> 01:51:11,770
可失败了
I failed.

1311
