我们为什么摔跤
Why do we fall, sir?

1312
01:51:17,490 --> 01:51:20,950
是为了学会自己爬起来
So that we can learn to pick ourselves up.

1313
01:51:23,450 --> 01:51:25,580
还没对我丧失信心吗
You still haven't given up on me?

1314
01:51:27,500 --> 01:51:28,960
从来没有
Never.

1315
01:51:30,040 --> 01:51:31,340
趴下
Down!

1316
01:51:31,540 --> 01:51:34,460
滥用暴力  警察滥用暴力
Harassment! I see harassment!

1317
01:51:34,630 --> 01:51:36,670
也许你想见识更暴力的  是吗
Maybe you'd like to see some excessive force?

1318
01:51:36,880 --> 01:51:38,760
拿枪的疯子
Madman with a gun.

1319
01:51:39,970 --> 01:51:44,990
警察全力围捕犯人  场面非常混乱  愤怒的居民情绪有些失控
With residents furious at the unprecedented show of police strength to round up the inmates

1320
01:51:44,990 --> 01:51:46,850
小姐  我们马上要升桥了
We're about to raise these bridges.

1321
01:51:47,060 --> 01:51:50,650
警官  我是哥谭市检察院的  让我过去
Officer, I am a Gotham City district attorney. Let me pass.

1322
01:51:58,070 --> 01:52:00,320
- 你给我闭嘴  - 嗨  弗拉斯  冷静
- Just shut up!  - Hey, Flass, cool it!

1323
01:52:00,530 --> 01:52:01,780
把这些人挡回去
Hold these people back.

1324
01:52:01,990 --> 01:52:04,990
嗨  戈登  有人要见你
Hey, Gordon. Somebody here to see you.

1325
01:52:05,160 --> 01:52:06,140
你来这干什么
What are you doing here?

1326
01:52:06,140 --> 01:52:07,540
我们共同的朋友让我交给你
Our friend sent me with this.

1327
01:52:07,750 --> 01:52:09,210
它能解克瑞恩的毒
It counteracts Crane's toxin.

1328
01:52:09,370 --> 01:52:10,830
希望你不会用到
Hopefully you won't need it.

1329
01:52:11,040 --> 01:52:14,170
除非有人能够把那玩意儿散到空气中
Not unless he's got some way of getting that crap into the air.

1330
01:52:15,340 --> 01:52:17,760
好吧 最后一辆过桥
All right, last one across.

1331
01:52:18,470 --> 01:52:22,350
好了各位  不到三分钟这桥就要升起来了
People, they want this bridge up in no more than three minutes!

1332
01:52:22,600 --> 01:52:25,930
你最好在大桥升起之前离开这个岛  巡警
Better get you off the island before they raise the bridges. Patrolman!

1333
01:52:26,600 --> 01:52:27,600
走
Go!

1334
01:52:54,420 --> 01:52:56,210
我找不到妈妈
I can't find my mom.

1335
01:52:56,590 --> 01:52:58,050
嗨
Hey!

1336
01:53:06,470 --> 01:53:08,180
你这是在干什么
What the hell are you doing?

1337
01:53:09,730 --> 01:53:11,270
先生们
Gentlemen

1338
01:53:11,730 --> 01:53:14,230
传达讯号的时间到了
time to spread the word.

1339
01:53:15,980 --> 01:53:17,360
这个讯号就是 
