我是洛布局长
This is Commissioner Loeb.

1346
01:54:44,030 --> 01:54:45,740
快点  那边的人快回话
Come on, somebody talk to me.

1347
01:54:45,910 --> 01:54:47,370
快啊
Come on!

1348
01:55:07,050 --> 01:55:09,050
听见吗  我是戈登
Loeb, Loeb. This is Gordon.

1349
01:55:09,390 --> 01:55:10,680
那儿在搞什么鬼
What the hell is going on?

1350
01:55:10,890 --> 01:55:14,310
我们需要增援  战术小组  特警  防暴警察
We need reinforcements. TAC teams, SWAT, riot cops!

1351
