谁说不会伤害
Of course they are!

1355
01:55:27,910 --> 01:55:28,910
克瑞恩
Crane?

1356
01:55:28,910 --> 01:55:30,910
不  稻草人
No. Scarecrow.

1357
01:55:32,660 --> 01:55:34,040
戈登
Gordon

1358
01:55:34,250 --> 01:55:36,460
我这儿已经派不出人了
there's nobody left to send in.

1359
01:55:38,040 --> 01:55:39,750
只剩下我一个
So I'm on my own?

1360
01:55:43,840 --> 01:55:45,460
纳罗斯岛快要被扯碎了
The Narrows is tearing itself to pieces.

1361
