Batman will save us. He'll come.

1376
01:57:03,880 --> 01:57:04,850
他会来的
He'll come.

1377
01:57:04,850 --> 01:57:05,850
别偷看
Don't peek.

1378
01:57:14,430 --> 01:57:17,770
我是戈登  准备把桥降下来
This is Gordon. Prepare to lower the bridge.

1379
01:57:23,690 --> 01:57:25,770
